window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>David and Vanesa are ready to call it quits. After five years of marriage, neither one of them can even stand to look at the other. But when a final, desperate attempt to save their marriage lands them in couples therapy, David and Vanesa are forced to look back on their roller coaster of a relationship and uncover where exactly they went wrong.</p> <p>Filled with humor and emotion and told through a set of flashbacks spanning their decade-long relationship, <i>Saying Goodbye</i> is a story about meeting the right person at the wrong time and fighting to make it work.</p> <p><b>Episode 1: \"Before the End of the World\"</b></p> <p>While attending their first session of couples therapy, David and Vanesa reminisce about the first time they met—at an \"End of the World Party\" more than a decade prior.</p> <p><b>Episode 2: \"Dating-ish\"</b></p> <p>As the session continues, David and Vanesa recount the moment they became more than just friends … and how Vanesa struggled with putting a label on their relationship.</p> <p><b>Episode 3: \"Like Romeo &amp; Juliet\"</b></p> <p>It's 2015, and Vanesa and David are together … but still not putting a label on things. After a night of drinking with friends, David decides to take a big swing in his relationship with Vanesa.</p> <p><b>Episode 4: \"Let's Get Hitched\"</b></p> <p>A year later, Vanesa is engaged to David and celebrating her 25th birthday. But when a surprise guest shows up to her party, Vanesa makes an (another) impulsive decision.</p> <p><b>Episode 5: \"The Big Mistake\"</b></p> <p>David and Vanesa describe the moment their relationship hit a rough patch. After two years of marriage and one major argument, David makes a choice he can never take back.</p> <p><b>Episode 6: \"Nobody Puts Baby in a Corner\"</b></p> <p>A year after his mistake, David is still legally married to Vanesa, but they're living separate lives. But a new opportunity presented to Vanesa might just make that separation official.</p> <p><b>Episode 7: \"Llévame contigo\"</b></p> <p>As Vanesa flourishes in LA, a potential new suitor enters the picture. Meanwhile, back in New York, David struggles to move on.</p> <p><b>Episode 8: \"Amor eterno\"</b></p> <p>David travels to LA to sign the divorce papers, but an undeniable spark between the couple forces them to reconsider their decision. In the present, a sudden bombshell rocks Vanesa and David's world.</p>"; 
